			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Ulma, the leader of Gur Tribe, talks to Astarion-avatar. Gur Hunter from Act 1, if he is alive, also present.&#xD;&#xA;Scene Trigger - WYR_GurCamp_Intro_SceneTrigger_8c9acc78-9d97-4d0f-919e-3997c015ed7f" />
